The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Shearer linked to England role

Buehlertal: Former England captain Alan Shearer could join the national teams coaching staff when Steve McClaren takes over as coach. 

British newspapers reported on Friday that Shearer, who retired at the end of last season, has been asked to join Englands coaching staff. McClaren takes over from Sven-Goran Eriksson after the World Cup. (AP) 




